No. 10-16. Jubani Agostin aka Zef Gjon Volaj, Petitioner v. Eric H. Holder, Jr., Attorney General. 562 U.S. 952, 131 S. Ct. 224,

178 L. Ed. 2d 250,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7836. October 4, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 363 Fed. Appx. 107.
